apiDescription: Bitwise nand with the current value, returning the previous value. The stabilized version of this intrinsic is available on the std::sync::atomic::AtomicBool type via the fetch_nand method by passing Ordering::Acquire as the order. For example, AtomicBool::fetch_nand.
